# PodOOMKilledAlert

## Meaning

This alert is based on an alerting when the pods gets restarted due to the reason OOM Killed

<details>
<summary>OOM Killed</summary>
* Pods will gets restrated with many reasons. One of them would be the OOM Killed.
* OOM Killed :  It occurs when there is a shortage of memory in the Pod to process the messages or task.
</details>
